headline: Chipotle Mexican Grill (CMG) Gets Price-Target Increase From Wealth-Management Firm
summary: Wealth-management firm Bernstein recently raised its price target on Chipotle Mexican Grill, Inc. (NYSE:CMG) to $65 from $60. headline: 3 High-Flying Stocks with Impressive Fundamentals
